{"tid":508092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙國家打吡逢加獨   皇家馬德里與巴塞隆拿球迷爆罵戰","createTime":"2017-12-24T02:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T03:01:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9b4c823831ba11848edac49ae10608151dcb9a","tid":508092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】皇家馬德里與巴塞隆拿本已是世仇，近期加泰隆尼亞的獨立風波更令兩軍球迷勢成水火。正值加泰議會補選的敏感時刻，西甲又上演國家打吡，佔得主場之利的皇家馬德里，一眾球迷賽前自然不會放過「熱情」招呼巴塞隆拿球員的機會。<br />\n<br />\n據西班牙傳媒報道，巴塞隆拿大軍抵達馬德里後，一下車就已被守候在球場附近的主隊球迷謾罵，其中多次與皇馬球迷爆發罵戰的巴塞主將碧基，就被皇馬球迷侮辱為「妓女」，而美斯下車時，在場的皇馬球迷則高呼美斯宿敵「C朗」名字諷刺。此外，他們又高呼要巴塞球員列隊歡迎剛贏得世冠盃的皇馬球員，不過最終兩軍以普通方式進場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171224/s00085/2d5ed30f9efc90b9b18fe65be473bdb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171224%2Fs00085%2F2d5ed30f9efc90b9b18fe65be473bdb2.jpg&h=9f7fa08d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c8fc74eddda1da8bb2d9c5f206ee0eb013c6050","tid":508092,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"主場輸3粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79f62d6bebf210bb5a312b55462fc44aae38c44","tid":508092,"uid":92002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:31:23.000Z","msg":"蝗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaceb605bad79fc51579dc4b554220e50395ac25","tid":508092,"uid":6728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c8fc74eddda1da8bb2d9c5f206ee0eb013c6050","tid":508092,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"主場輸3粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"仲要人列隊拍掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 